premise_source_doc_sentence: The song marks the second coming for Pitbull by Ne-Yo , following the smash-hit `` Give Me Everything ''  (  2011  )  ; co-producers Dr. Luke and Cirkut also mark their fourth joint production for Pitbull  (  after `` Timber '' , `` Wild Wild Love '' , and `` We Are One  (  Ole Ola  )  ''  )  and third for Ne-Yo  (  after `` She Knows '' and T-Pain 's `` Turn All the Lights On ''  )  .
